title: In Control
tags: 2002 Demo EBM Lyrics Lyrics-Incomplete Mekka&Symposium video Vocals Windows
info:
Why is it that the sadness wouldn't leave,
That there's always something cold in this warm world of mine?
Every sun ray seems to hurt; flowers fade as I walk by.
This small itch when I think everything's just fine.

So why don't I feel the contentment, the happiness I am supposed to feel?
Why do I still dwell in compassion, denying to see that my dream's come real?
I just want to finally realise I'm in control of what I'll become,
Without need of asking the world while still here and not long gone.

Come on!
